@syntax flex
@targets html

Create a beautiful landing page for a fictional AI startup called "MindFlow AI". 
The page should have a modern, sleek design with a gradient background.
Include a hero section with the company name and tagline "Empowering Intelligence, Amplifying Innovation".
Add a features section showcasing three key features with icons and descriptions.
Include a contact form at the bottom where visitors can enter their email to get updates.
Make it fully responsive and add smooth scroll animations when sections come into view.